
## Plot Styles
Colors, font size, line thickness, all have default values in Matplotlib. In addition to the default style for these plot attributes, additional styles are available to apply to Matplotlib plots.
To use the default style, either don't specify a style at all or use the line ```plt.style.use('default')```.  Remember, if using a Jupyter notebook include the line ```%matplotlib inline```
